      <title>特鲁多警告加拿大企业推迟气候投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/canadian-firms-are-delaying-climate-investments-trudeau-is-warned</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一份新报告警告说，加拿大在实现 2030 年排放目标方面面临着“关键问题”，因为由于该国气候政策未来的不确定性，企业正在推迟建设低碳项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/canadian-firms-are-delaying-climate-investments-trudeau-is-warned</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
