      <title>欧洲咖啡贸易商敦促欧盟推迟森林砍伐规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/europe-s-coffee-traders-urge-eu-to-delay-deforestation-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲咖啡行业敦促欧盟推迟实施其开创性的森林砍伐规则，理由是这可能对数百万种植者造成毁灭性影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-22/europe-s-coffee-traders-urge-eu-to-delay-deforestation-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Feb 2024 10:59:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
